		<h2>Lightcubes</h2>
		<p>Lightcubes is a concept/prototype for an interactive sculpture which monitors outside lighting conditions and provides a kinetic display of reflected light, which has a variant visibility dependent on the amount of artificial lighting within a room. The goal is to provide awareness of using energy for artifical light when natural light outside is already sufficient.</p>


